The evil Archwizard Ashkenazy has been scheming up 
some great plans in his tower... some say he will 
soon rule all of Darkwind! Reports of massive armies 
being built and mobilized for the final confrontation
with the puny inhabitants of Darkwind. Many foolhardy
 adventurers have claimed to have defeated Ashkenazy, 
but as many lickings as he takes, he just keeps on 
ticking! Find a way to stop Ashkenazy, before it is 
too late!

This is a lower level quest, but requires much exploring.
